<https://w3id.org/narn/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An OWL ontology for modeling story plots and narrative structures. It provides a formal vocabulary to represent characters, locations, events, actions, and temporal relations within a narrative."@en .
